nce profiling.<ref>[http://www.silexlabs.org/amfphp-2-2-profiler-released/ Amfphp 2.2 Profiler is out!<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref> * version 2.2.1 is released in August 2014.<ref>[http://www.silexlabs.org/amfphp-2-2-1-released/ Amfphp 2.2.1 Profiler is out!<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref> * version 2.2.2 is released in January 2016.<ref>[http://www.silexlabs.org/updates-for-amfphp-and-baguette-amf/ Updates for Amfphp and Baguette AMF<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>
